| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4923 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 406e3f98-52b2-5ddb-a3ac-4ec952e293f0"
